methods.canonicalize:
Canonicalize this tuple.

:param canonicalizer: (java.util.function.UnaryOperator<java.lang.Object>) - The canonicalization operator to use on each object element.
:return: (CanonicalizableTuple.TUPLE_TYPE) This tuple if already canonical, else a new, canonical tuple of the same type

text:
Interface for immutable tuple classes that can produce a new instance of themselves with canonicalized object
 elements.
